<p>
  <%= link_to "機能一覧",  feature_root_path %>
  -> スプラトゥーン2連携「イラスト投稿でのドットの自動打ち」
  -> <%= link_to "スケッチ一覧",  feature_splatoon2_sketches_path %>
  -> <%= link_to "スケッチ「#{@sketch.name}」",  feature_splatoon2_sketches_path(@sketch) %>
  -> <%= "デバイス「#{@device.name}」" %>
  -> <%= "デバイスに送信する" %>
</p>

<h1>デバイスに送信する</h1>
<div class="hide"
     data-controller="splatoon2-sketch-drawer"
     data-splatoon2-sketch-drawer-data-value="<%= @binarization_macros.to_json %>"
     data-splatoon2-sketch-drawer-request_path-value="<%= feature_splatoon2_sketch_device_drawing_sketch_path(@sketch.id, @device.unique_key) %>">
  ステータス: <span data-splatoon2-sketch-drawer-target="status"></span><br>
  進捗率: <span data-splatoon2-sketch-drawer-target="progress"></span><br>
  書き込み中のポジション: <span data-splatoon2-sketch-drawer-target="position"></span>
  <hr>
  送信インターバル(msec): <input type="text" value="1000" data-splatoon2-sketch-drawer-target="send_interval"><br><br>
  <button class="btn btn-primary" data-action="click->splatoon2-sketch-drawer#start">書き込む</button>
  <button class="btn btn-success" data-action="click->splatoon2-sketch-drawer#reset">最初に戻る</button>
  <button class="btn btn-danger" data-action="click->splatoon2-sketch-drawer#stop">停止する</button>
</div>

<hr>

書き込み対象<br>

<img border="1" data-controller="splatoon2-sketches" data-splatoon2-sketches-image-path-value="<%= cropped_monochrome_image_feature_splatoon2_sketch_path(@sketch.id) %>">
